thread.title_full: Fans vote Bethlehem Catholic's Antwon Keenan as Lehigh Valley's best RB

title: Fans vote Bethlehem Catholic's Antwon Keenan as Lehigh Valley's best RB
text:
Bethlehem Catholic running back Antwon Keenan makes a cut against Liberty. (lehighvalleylive.com file photo) By Greg Joyce | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 07, 2015 8:00 AM 
The votes are in and the fans have selected Bethlehem Catholic 's Antwon Keenan as the Lehigh Valley's best running back. 
The senior earned 25 percent of the voting to lead the 21 candidates. 
Through five games this year, Keenan has taken 62 carries for 718 yards and 17 touchdowns. 
Stay tuned for the next fan vote to pick the Lehigh Valley's top wide receiver.
